  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0baf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f \u0baa\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc7?",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Where are the journalists arrested by the army?",
      "author": "Rajeeban",
      "body_lines": [
        "There are reports that many journalists who were reporting on the attack by the army on the protestors in Khalimugat were attacked, while it is not known what happened to the two journalists who were arrested.",
        "There are reports that the soldiers have not yet handed over Chathuranga Pradeep Kumar and Kasun Kumarage to the police who were arrested in Kollupitiya Krasgat area.",
        "Demonstrators have been attacked, including BBC journalist Geraine Samuel and a number of anti-racism lawyers."
      ],
